snippet.title: Beyond Galaxyland Release Date Trailer - Future Games Show Gamescom 2024
snippet.description:
A new trailer for Beyond Galaxyland revealed that the retro-futurist fantasy RPG will be released later this year on September 24 for PC and consoles.

https://www.youtube.com/@FutureGamesShow

#Beyondgalaxyland #FutureGamesShow #FGS #futuregamesshow2024 #gamescom
